org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter

Interface HintingFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ColumnPrefixFilter, ColumnRangeFilter, FuzzyRowFilter, MultipleColumnPrefixFilter, MultiRowRangeFilter, PrefixFilter, TimestampsFilter

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
public interface HintingFilter
    Marker interface for filters that may return SEEK_NEXT_USING_HINT. This marker interface indicates that when it's used in a MUST_PASS_ALL FilterList then filterCell() must always be called if filterRowKey() returned false.
